<plot>Some things in life change you. Some test you... Father Samuel's world is left unbalanced after a young man confesses horrible acts to him. He is disturbed by what he has heard and unable to absolve the man of his guilt. The young priest tries to forget the man's sins but soon finds himself haunted by them; his faith is shaken as he realizes the personal consequence of the man's actions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?017084</url></doc>
